{"tid":249534,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[i大仔入一入] [認真] 有無人試過比i大老師針對？","createTime":"2017-05-19T11:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T01:41:51.000Z","uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1898e98afe4d23cf19e3c22bc9d3d3cb1c6ac6e6","tid":249534,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:12:33.000Z","msg":"滑雪我今年i大既year 2 咁我地有個final year project<br />\n咁就係係學校入面搞d活動例如平衡車 密室逃脫咁引d傻仔比錢玩<br />\n咁就搞左兩日 兩日我都有返<br />\n但今日個濕鳩主任話我無返同我個試卷好低分要retake呢科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我d 朋友就覺得佢係有心做鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先呢科個試卷根本唔重要 你幾低分都一定拉到你合格<br />\n第二我個試卷我肯定我合格 我甚至敢叫佢拎返份卷叫佢比我睇 如果我真係好低分我乜柒都得<br />\n第三我果日有返 屌佢老母佢話我無撚出現過<br />\n<br />\n真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人類似呢d情況<br />\n應該點做好我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661b21482e1163d83115ed618aefb3d6dabea7c9","tid":249534,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:16:39.000Z","msg":"我知佢係要搞鳩我佢大把理由做我<br />\n你話我無做野又好 點都好<br />\n你比到個合理原因我都可以硬食左佢<br />\n反正你條撚樣一向都唔撚妥我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌佢老味佢係學系主任 一人之下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都唔好咁撚莫須有<br />\n屈鳩我做返都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"ddb3e0884cd2727944a3f43daed512169e882665","tid":249534,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我知佢係要搞鳩我佢大把理由做我<br />\n你話我無做野又好 點都好<br />\n你比到個合理原因我都可以硬食左佢<br />\n反正你條撚樣一向都唔撚妥我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a